headline: It’s Earnings Warning Season. How to Profit From Others’ Misery.
summary: Lululemon’s management is under pressure. It is reasonable to expect they will use January to tidy up their affairs and reset investor expectations.

headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid REGN and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: What a fantastic six months it’s been for Regeneron. Shares of the company have skyrocketed 47.6%, hitting $774.98. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
